run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7cbe2ba7088e9995188a7a164b63807320512a","tid":2487944,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be82b079f77702cb7344ce4fe49a00277f62c42c","tid":2487944,"uid":55519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8ff494038b616951e8443600ab6721b894e18f7","tid":2487944,"uid":137569,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:36:03.000Z","msg":"仲閪過Irene<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:50:05.000Z","msg":"真係一山還有一山高"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"係一閪還有一閪西"},{"pid":"41d73722b2c07d4c9778febff531a44eeac48448","tid":2487944,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf197b43863be963ac816e0bd8cfc180b5aa54c","tid":2487944,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:11:57.000Z","msg":"南韓演員徐睿知和金正賢的對話遭爆出，其中最讓韓網詫異的是「你不和工作人員打招呼是對的」，也因為這樣造成了人品議論。一名自稱曾與徐共事的工作人員（下稱A某）14日凌晨在Pann寫下長文，爆料對方完全不將工作人員當人看：「把我們當狗豬一樣藐視。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564041.jpg&h=671a1675&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲徐睿知因金正賢事件遭連環爆出負面新聞。（圖／翻攝自GOLDMEDALIST）<br />\n<br />\nA某14日於Pann發文，標題寫下「曾共事的工作人員爆料演員徐睿知的人品」，文內指出徐睿知完全不管二手菸問題都會在車上抽菸，髒話掛嘴邊，不只如此只要她去哪工作人員就得跟上，如果她心情不好不吃飯，那工作人員也不能吃：「因為演員都沒吃了。」<br />\n<br />\n而且，A某在拍攝前一天被徐睿知緊抓著聊天不放，只睡了1、2個小時，隔天忍不住睡意就被罵，為了醒腦吃糖又被罵「妳算老幾竟敢在演員工作時吃糖果」。A某更指出徐睿知因為個性差，所以單拍一個作品就換了好幾個經紀人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564040.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564040.jpg&h=abb016eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲徐睿知遭爆常罵髒話還會在車內抽菸。（圖／翻攝自GOLDMEDALIST）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，A某也提到徐睿知非常自戀：「說是要愛自己負責的演員，要我們（工作人員）的手機桌布都放妳的照片，如果有妳的新聞就要我們去留言稱讚好漂亮、演技真好，還把我們的帳號背下來碎念『怎麼都寫一樣的，也寫點別的』，真的非常厭煩，而且還要我們加入妳的Fan Cafe，明明這麼愛自己，怎麼就沒辦法愛給身邊的人？」<br />\n<br />\n爆料文的最後，A某附上徐睿知在宣傳《另有他路》上《朴善英的Cinetown》的腳本，還有徐睿知的親筆簽名，她還強調：「（徐睿知）本身就很自戀，所以就算沒跟她要簽名也會自己簽（給工作人員）。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564044.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564044.jpg&h=2ffa1811&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5564/d5564045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5564%2Fd5564045.jpg&h=e350188f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲A某附上腳本和簽名以證明自己所言不假。（圖／翻攝自Pann）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:52:47.000Z","msg":"佢是一個好強大的控制狂。。。。。。應該患了ＯＣＤ"},{"pid":"a61c911bb155d433813ae96cda9174d93c065630","tid":2487944,"uid":358691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:55:48.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />女皇格、樣靚、波大、腰細、腿長、皮膚白滑，仲要識西文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c2922d87a0e4cd2d917b5d68938b12045c90b1","tid":2487944,"uid":92353,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"好樣衰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要個樣又老"},{"pid":"b011938b22b655e5596f90dab7b01db10ff5dc15","tid":2487944,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e2d1c31e8c3e94cf7e2f38cfaa3fd963648ec97d","tid":2487944,"uid":170,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"d92888f784a8ba7113009d2eab56da74e98c0443","tid":2487944,"uid":24596,"like":101,"dislike":0,"score":101,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"佢拍精神病個套箅唔算係做緊自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:25:51.000Z","msg":"定係太入戲，精神病佢做得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T0